These ETFs will be structured as open-ended funds meaning they can create or redeem shares based on investor demand. This will allow each ETF to maintain a close correlation to the price of Bitcoin by adjusting its holdings as necessary.

A spot Bitcoin ETF is an investment vehicle that provides investors with exposure to the price movements of Bitcoin. It tracks the performance of Bitcoin by holding actual Bitcoin itself rather than derivative contracts or futures.
